image_analysis.description: A photograph showing a clear plastic storage bin filled with several white and yellow boxes. The boxes appear to contain hard drives, as indicated by the printed images of hard drives on the box lids. Yellow 'EVIDENCE' tape is used to seal the boxes. The bin is sitting inside what looks like a cabinet or storage locker. To the right, another plastic bin is partially visible containing blue folders or binders.
